<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–12" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 9 - 12. Megischus kuafu Ge &amp; Tan, sp. nov. Holotype ♀ 9 hind coxa, lateral view 10 hind femur, lateral view 11 hind tibia, lateral view 12 hind tarsi, lateral view." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1022.62833.figures9-12" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/517763" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">11</figureCitation>
