<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">Colour</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Mostly black; mesosoma, metasoma, antennae, and hind legs black or blackish; head dark reddish brown; tergite II brownish bilaterally; wing membrane light brownish, hyaline, except most of hind portion of first subdiscal cell and apical part of hind wing brown; veins and pterostigma brown or dark brown; fore and middle legs dark brown (except for coxae black); ovipositor sheath largely black and with whitish subapical band.
</paragraph>
